{"tid":1167843,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"任正非：Arm暫停合作對華為沒影響","createTime":"2019-05-23T09:55:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T13:59:51.000Z","uid":211600,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"890f008327f08eee845f136ae702e3981481587f","tid":1167843,"uid":211600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T09:55:24.000Z","msg":"据财联社报道，今日，华为CEO任正非对媒体表示，美国出口管制导致Arm暂停与华为合作，对华为「没有影响」，华为公司已经获得Arm架构的永久授权。<br />\n<br />\n他认为，Arm母公司日本软银集团正在寻求美国政府同意，使旗下电信运营商Sprint能与T-Mobile合并，如果此时违背美国意愿，会受到很大损失。<br />\n<br />\n此前，Arm中国曾表示，十分重视长期合作伙伴海思，正在积极寻求合规的妥善解决方案。"},{"pid":"fe107b8f4d645a5f0260d3f41f95331764927903","tid":1167843,"uid":254259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T09:59:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a53b30b5ac9edbe742dae88e277202bbf6f1a1dd","tid":1167843,"uid":522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T10:01:52.000Z","msg":"華為: 版權不適用於中國大陸"},{"pid":"cc3895490167118f81dfd7433baaaac64fa4bc79","tid":1167843,"uid":202137,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T10:03:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dvR1cKb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdvR1cKb.jpg&h=17a3c293&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"13e834e0c017c9d173c5e821631afbfe84ff9db9","tid":1167843,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T10:04:57.000Z","msg":"現有架構永久授權炸<br />\n係咪諗住到2023年都係用2019年架構<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caa7455753bcf1e06a6d8e611eb9e30218b3d7fb","tid":1167843,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:59:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}